<br>
To both Vainne and Darbok, burning religious symbols or even the flag, No matter how much you dislike it or are offended by it, they are both still legal. You have every right to legally react to any such person doing things that you find offensive, but you can't take away their right to do such things. As soon as you do you destroy the ammendment. <br>
<br>
I served in the military. I had friends I've seen laid in the ground with a flag atop their coffin. I raised the flag hundreds of times, I still get a tear in my eye when I hear the National Anthem, I was extraordinarily angry when I learned the National Endowment of the Arts gave a grant to a guy who put a crucifix in a jar of urine! Why do I mention this? Because despite my feelings about all of these subjects I wouldn't want anyone who felt they 'knew better' than me to come along and tell me what I could and couldn't burn or put in a jar of urine 'for my own good'. <br>
<br>
Freedom of Speech isn't easy. It's too easy to say what <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>YOU</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> think should be the limits. Who the hell are <br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>YOU</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->? And what the hell are <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>YOU</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> gonna do when someday you become a part of <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>THEM</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> and not <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>US</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->?<br>
Because by instituting limits on the Freedom of Speech suddenly it isn't a freedom any longer. GWB said something incredibly stupid since he became president, was shown to me on one of the many websites that like to make fun of him : &quot;There ought to be limits to freedoms&quot;. Holy Cow! I never had much love for the ACLU but I hope to god that set off a five alarm fire in their offices. <br>
<br>
The funny thing is, those who are arguing that their ought to be limits are well within their rights to argue such things. Perhaps if their limits were put in place, we wouldn't be having this discussion.  <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub40.ezboard.com/fthesaryrntavernthefurnace.showMessageRange?topicID=3251.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a><a href=http://pub40.ezboard.com/fthesaryrntavernthefurnace.showMessageRange?topicID=3251.topic&start=21&stop=40>2</a> <b>3</b> <a href=http://pub40.ezboard.com/fthesaryrntavernthefurnace.showMessageRange?topicID=3251.topic&start=61&stop=80>4</a><a href=http://pub40.ezboard.com/fthesaryrntavernthefurnace.showMessageRange?topicID=3251.topic&start=81&stop=96>5</a> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub40.ezboard.com/fthesaryrntavernthefurnace.showPrevMessage?topicID=3251.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub40.ezboard.com/fthesaryrntavernthefurnace.showNextMessage?topicID=3251.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub40.ezboard.com/fthesaryrntavernthefurnace.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3251.topic&index=60><img src=http://members.cox.net/cbilyeu/tavern/notnice_reply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub40.ezboard.com/fthesaryrntavernthefurnace.emailToFriend?topicID=3251.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub40.ezboard.com/fthesaryrntavernthefurnace.threadControl?topicID=3251.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/grunge/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub40.ezboard.com/fthesaryrntavernthefurnace.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=3251.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 